Privacy Policy for M21 Sport MM

Welcome to M21 Sport MM! 

This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and handle user data. It is important to us that you understand the information we collect and how we use it.

Information We Collect:

We collect the following registration information:

User-provided information during the registration process, including but not limited to name, email address, and any additional information voluntarily provided.

How We Collect Information:

We collect registration information when:

Users voluntarily provide information during the registration process.

How We Use Information:

We use the collected information for the following purposes:

To create and manage user accounts so users can buy their sport products.

Data Sharing:

We do not share personal or sensitive user data with any third parties, including third-party service providers, advertisers, etc.

Data Security:

We employ secure data handling procedures to protect personal and sensitive user data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

Data Retention and Deletion:

Data Deletion Policy

Purpose

This document sets out our policy for responding to requests for deletion of data. This document explains the rights of the data subject in relation to data deletion and the responsibilities of M21 Sport MM Co., Ltd in responding to such a request.

Individual Rights

An individual has the right to erasure, also known as the right to be forgotten. The principle underpinning this right is to enable an individual to request the deletion or removal of personal data where there is no compelling reason for its continued processing.

Data Deletion Request

Our Service may give you the ability to delete certain information about you from within the Service. You may update, amend, or delete your information at any time by signing in to your Account, if you have one, and visiting the account settings section that allows you to manage your personal information.

You can request to delete your data from our systems by the following steps:

Sign in to your Account.

Click "My Profile," and navigate to "Delete Account."

In the Delete Account section, select the reason for deletion.

Then, click "Delete My Account."

If you wish to have your personal information deleted from our systems, you can submit a data deletion request by contacting us at care@shopdoora.com or wailinn@mypetmm.com, or through our data deletion request form.

How Can Data Be Deleted?

A user of M21 Sport MM can delete the user account upon request (via email to wailinn@mypetmm.com). This data is deleted from the system immediately and cannot be recovered by any users or M21 Sport MM employees after this point. Data that has been deleted or otherwise destroyed cannot be recovered at any time. Sufficient warning is given to the account administrator before data is permanently deleted. Data may still remain in the systemâ€™s backup files, which will be deleted periodically.

Data Deletion Timeline

Information may be deleted from our eCommerce system upon request to wailinn@mypetmm.com. We undertake to perform the deletion within one month (30 calendar days) and will send you a confirmation once the information has been deleted. Wherever possible, we aim to complete the request in advance of the deadline.

What Information Does M21 Sport MM Retain?

M21 Sport MM stores data about individuals in order to create a report. We store names, email addresses, and subsequent order information for each individual to create a report, which is stored on our secure servers in Myanmar. These data are stored and used in accordance with our Privacy Policy. If consent is provided, personal data (including the above, plus address, telephone number, and notes) may be stored in our eCommerce system for the purposes of contacting you regarding M21 Sport MM news, products, and promotions.

Contact Information:

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your privacy, you can contact us at:

By email: care@shopdoora.com, wailinn@mypetmm.com

Privacy Policy Accessibility:

This privacy policy is accessible through the following channels:

In the app registration form, we include a checkbox to agree to our privacy policy. Users can click the link to read it before creating an account.

Non-Editable and Readable:

This privacy policy is non-editable and readable in a standard browser without any plugins or special handlers (no PDFs).

Entity Reference:

This privacy policy refers to the entity named in the app's Google Play listing as M21 Sport MM.

By using M21 Sport MM, you agree to the terms outlined in this privacy policy. We may update this policy periodically, so please review it regularly. Your continued use of the app after any changes to this policy constitutes your acceptance of those changes.

